text: This is a list of 2013 events that occurred in Moldova. ==Incumbents== *President: Nicolae Timofti *Prime Minister: Vlad Filat (until 25 April), Iurie Leancă (starting 25 April) *President of the Parliament: Marian Lupu (until 25 April), Liliana Palihovici (25 April–30 May), Igor Corman (starting 30 May) ==Events== Moldova in the Eurovision Song Contest 2013. ==References==
title: 2013 in Moldova
